  "monster": {
    "title": "Joace.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Joace has an armoured green body with strange knobs attached and a cow's skull for a head.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 188     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: +++      </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++ ++  </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: +         </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: +..     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ∞        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><darkgrey>rElec: .        </darkgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 180% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 92% to hit with your +9 broad axe of flaming and 92% to hit with your headbutt.\nIt has about 36% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     35          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting Joace.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
